title: Apply Now !
posting_body: ['Oaks of Baytown Apartments', '2011 Ward Rd, Baytown, TX, 77520', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 48', 'OR Text', '48', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team directly.', 'Use this link for more information:', '<URL>', 'Love Where You Live!', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 713 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Oaks of Baytown is best known for its beautiful landscaping and spacious one, two and three bedroom apartments.', 'Outside, we invite you to float in the sparkling pool, bask in the sun or relax on the beautiful grounds.', 'Our friendly and knowledgeable staff is more than happy to assist with all of your needs.', 'Send us an email anytime and receive a timely response to any question you might have.', 'There is so much that the Oaks of Baytown community has to offer you.', 'So come experience all of the reasons why you should make Oaks of Baytown your new home today!', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet Friendly, No weight limit, No breed restriction dogs and cats only*', 'Income Requirements:', 'Must make 3 times the monthly rent.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:8:30AM-5:30PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-4:00PM', 'ntHZWKE0g8']
